===Etymology===
Named after its inventor [[w:Madeleine Paulmier|Madeleine Paulmier]], 19th century pastry cook.

===Noun===
#A small [[gateau]] or sponge [[cake]], usually shaped like an elongated scallop shell; well-known as a mnemonic device invoked by Marcel Proust's character in <cite>A la recherche du temps perdu</cite> (<cite>Remembrance of Things Past</cite>).